modules.source:
"mixin og-meta(data)
  meta(property='og:title' content=data.title || project.title)
  meta(property='og:type' content='article')
  meta(property='og:url' content=project.repository.url)
  meta(property='og:image' content=data.image || 'TODO: Share image')
  meta(property='og:description' content=data.description || 'TODO: Describe Me')
  meta(property='og:site_name' content=data.site_name || project.title)
"

modules.name: ./node_modules/jade-loader/stringify.loader.js!./app/mixins/twitter-meta.jade
modules.source:
"mixin twitter-meta(data)
  meta(name='twitter:card' content='summary_large_image')
  meta(name='twitter:site' content='@intelsoftware')
  meta(name='twitter:creator' content='@'+data.account)
  meta(name='twitter:title' content=data.title)
  meta(name='twitter:description' content=data.description)
  meta(name='twitter:image' content=data.image)
"

modules.source:
"include ../mixins/link
include ../mixins/og-meta
include ../mixins/twitter-meta

block config
  - var pageTitle = 'Jade | CSSNext | Babel'

doctype html
html
  include ../partials/head

  block title
    title= pageTitle

  link(rel='stylesheet' href='/css/#{htmlWebpackPlugin.options.page}.css')

  body
    block content

    script(src='/js/#{htmlWebpackPlugin.options.page}.js' async)
"
